{"tid":212601,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[0度左右]求推介保暖既羽絨","createTime":"2017-04-22T14:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T00:28:59.000Z","uid":90690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae29f5266d37592f2ca22f26d0715334265b3bf","tid":212601,"uid":90690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"如題 遲D去旅行, 最高海拔既地方可能最凍0度左右,<br />\nuniqlo 羽絨係咪一定唔夠頂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bdbda35d26aaeeb8405dc4b41083d9f9af1941","tid":212601,"uid":90690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545c7ce8f65d0977cd0a89211e3bb7e64d5ecf1f","tid":212601,"uid":38679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T16:13:15.000Z","msg":"0度都唔凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Uniqlo夠啦"},{"pid":"19e740a1a2169fce2033ae3e4f0c1c16d0bdc666","tid":212601,"uid":90690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43011286a1f6b5892591543b632634f72aaeef28","tid":212601,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"香港濕凍係全世界最凍"},{"pid":"d5858cd35955197d11f7b9cd2f7e9045d5820447","tid":212601,"uid":90690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"da3bd493bf449cc547ff70aee2cb9d8c6d079bb0","tid":212601,"uid":90690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80637940b9922e0119b1c69aafba3d9b6220d6f2","tid":212601,"uid":53668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"就咁0度唔凍㗎，日頭有少少太陽大褸已經得。<br />\n所以要睇埋風速同濕度，大風加落少少雨就算十度都凍到仆街<br />\n但零度一定要帶手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}